chart.name: Current Sessions
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.session_current', filter=filter('service_name', 'BACKEND', 'FRONTEND')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_session_current', filter=filter('service_name', 'BACKEND', 'FRONTEND')).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Sessions Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.session_rate_all').publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_session_rate_all').publish(label='B')

chart.description: Ratio of system polling time versus total time over the last minute
chart.name: Idle Percent
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.idle_pct', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).mean(over='1m').publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_idle_percent', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).mean(over='1m').publish(label='B')

chart.name: 2xx, 4xx, 5xx Responses
chart.programText:
C = data('derive.response_5xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='C')
B = data('derive.response_4xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')
A = data('derive.response_2xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
D = data('haproxy_response_5xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='D')
E = data('haproxy_response_4xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='E')
F = data('haproxy_response_2xx', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Bytes In
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.bytes_in', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_bytes_in', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Session Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.session_rate', filter=filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_session_rate', filter=filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND')).publish(label='B')

chart.description: Average response time from a server in milliseconds, over the last 1024 requests
chart.name: Average Response Time
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.response_time_avg', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and (not filter('service_name', 'BACKEND'))).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_response_time_average', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and (not filter('service_name', 'BACKEND'))).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Bytes Out
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.bytes_out', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_bytes_out', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND')).publish(label='B')

chart.description: Number of times a request a connection to a server was retried and/or redispatched to another server
chart.name: Server Retries and Redispatches
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.retries', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
B = data('derive.redispatched', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')
C = data('haproxy_retries', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='C')
D = data('haproxy_redispatched', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='D')

chart.description: Number of items currently in backend queue
chart.name: Current Queue Size
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.queue_current', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_queue_current', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Requests per Second
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.requests', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_requests', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Request Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.error_request', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_error_request', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='B')

chart.description: Number of times a server has been selected in the last reporting interval
chart.name: Top Servers Selected
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.server_selected_total', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_server_selected_total', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='B')

chart.description: The average queue time in milliseconds over the past 1024 requests
chart.name: Average Queue Time
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.queue_time_avg', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_queue_time_average', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Connection Rate
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.connection_rate', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_connection_rate_all', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Connection Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.error_connection', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and (not filter('service_name', 'BACKEND')), rollup='delta').publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_error_connections', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and (not filter('service_name', 'BACKEND'))).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Response Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.error_response', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_error_response', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')

chart.description: Average session time in seconds over the past 1024 requests
chart.name: Average Session Time
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.session_time_avg').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A/1000).publish(label='B')
C = data('haproxy_session_time_average').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C/1000).publish(label='D')

chart.name: Denied Requests
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.denied_request', filter=filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND'), rollup='delta').publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_denied_request', filter=filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND'), rollup='delta').publish(label='B')

chart.name: Denied Responses
chart.programText:
A = data('derive.denied_response', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy'), rollup='delta').publish(label='A')
B = data('haproxy_denied_response', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Request Rate
chart.programText:

B = data('haproxy_request_rate', filter=filter('plugin', 'haproxy') and filter('service_name', 'FRONTEND')).publish(label='B')

chart.description: Number of times a server has been selected in the last reporting interval

chart.programText:

B = data('haproxy_server_selected_total', filter=(not filter('service_name', 'BACKEND')), rollup='delta').publish(label='B')
